                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.24/1679: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Gauss</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-12-22T22:00:00-04:00"
                            >December 22, 1943—10 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1841. (Reference Embassy’s 2429, December 16, 3 p.m.) In view of various recent
                    developments, this whole question is here under reconsideration. The Department
                    is, therefore, not at this moment in position to give you specific instructions
                    regarding action to be taken. As soon as it is in position to do so, Department
                    will further advise you.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
